OL,3,CBalmoral 'a uniquely special place in
OL,4,Cthe hearts of the royal family', says
OL,5,CKing
OL,7,FBalmoral holds a "uniquely special
OL,8,Fplace" in the hearts of the royal
OL,9,Ffamily, the King has said in the
OL,10,Fforeword to a new guidebook.
OL,12,FCharles, writing in the 80-page
OL,13,Fpaperback, said the Scottish estate is
OL,14,Fa "cherished home" for his family,
OL,15,Fwith "startling individuality" and a
OL,16,F"precious, almost sacred, surrounding
OL,17,Flandscape".
