OL,3,CBalmoral 'a uniquely special place in
OL,4,Cthe hearts of the royal family', says
OL,5,CKing
OL,7,FIn 1852, the Balmoral estate was
OL,8,Fpurchased by Queen Victoria and her
OL,9,Fhusband Prince Albert, who had fallen
OL,10,Fin love with the Highlands and went on
OL,11,Fto build the castle.
OL,13,FSince then, it has become a favourite
OL,14,Fsummer retreat of the royal family,
OL,15,Fwith kings and queens adding their own
OL,16,Fstamp to the castle and grounds over
OL,17,Fthe decades.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
