PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1780275788
OL,3,CBalmoral 'a uniquely special place in
OL,4,Cthe hearts of the royal family', says
OL,5,CKing
OL,7,FCharles wrote of the 50,000-acre
OL,8,Festate: "Balmoral has been the
OL,9,Fcherished Scottish home of my family
OL,10,Fsince the estate was purchased by
OL,11,FPrince Albert, my great-great-great-
OL,12,Fgrandfather, in 1852.
OL,14,F"With its buildings of startling
OL,15,Findividuality, which never fail to
OL,16,Ffascinate, and its precious, almost
OL,17,Fsacred, surrounding landscape, it is a
OL,18,Fplace where there is constant change,
OL,19,Fyet everything remains unaltered, with
OL,20,Fa sense of timelessness which
OL,21,Frefreshes the soul.
OL,26,@pD@IOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1780275788
OL,3,CBalmoral 'a uniquely special place in
OL,4,Cthe hearts of the royal family', says
OL,5,CKing
OL,7,F"Since my earliest childhood, it has
OL,8,Fheld, and continues to hold, a
OL,9,Funiquely special place in the hearts
OL,10,Fof my family and myself, and my late
OL,11,Fmother particularly treasured her time
OL,12,Fat Balmoral.
OL,14,F"It was here, in these most beloved of
OL,15,Fsurroundings, that she chose to spend
OL,16,Fher final days.
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1780275788
OL,3,CBalmoral 'a uniquely special place in
OL,4,Cthe hearts of the royal family', says
OL,5,CKing
OL,7,F"Whatever the circumstances in which
OL,8,Fyou are reading this book, I hope that
OL,9,Fyou, too, will be inspired by the rich
OL,10,Fcomplexity of the architecture and
OL,11,Fshare in the magic of the surrounding
OL,12,Fcountryside, whose 'wild and majestic'
OL,13,Flandscape has been the source of
OL,14,Finspiration and enjoyment for so many."
OL,16,FCharles's mother, Queen Elizabeth II,
OL,17,Fdied peacefully at the estate aged 96
OL,18,Fon September 8 2022 after serving as
OL,19,Fsovereign for 70 years
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@gO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
