OL,3,CBalmoral 'a uniquely special place in
OL,4,Cthe hearts of the royal family', says
OL,5,CKing
OL,7,FThe guidebook opens with an image of a
OL,8,Fwatercolour of the castle, painted by
OL,9,FCharles in 1989, alongside the
OL,10,Fforeword.
OL,12,FIn July 2024, the King opened the
OL,13,FAberdeenshire castle to the public for
OL,14,Fthe first time in more than 170 years
OL,15,Fand has made a number of changes to
OL,16,Fthe interior and the gardens.
OL,18,FBefore this, the only part of the
OL,19,Fbuilding the public could visit was
OL,20,Fthe ballroom, which houses a different
OL,21,Fexhibition each year.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
