PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1780275788
OL,3,CBalmoral 'a uniquely special place in
OL,4,Cthe hearts of the royal family', says
OL,5,CKing
OL,7,FPrime ministers are traditionally
OL,8,Finvited to stay with the head of state
OL,9,Fat Balmoral during the summer, and
OL,10,FHarold Wilson, who is said to have
OL,11,F"got on like a house on fire" with
OL,12,FQueen Elizabeth II, joined members of
OL,13,Fthe royal family for riverside picnics
OL,14,Fon the estate.
OL,16,FThe new guidebook, titled Balmoral and
OL,17,Fwritten by journalist and historian
OL,18,FMary Miers, details how the King
OL,19,Freplaced the ballroom lawn with an
OL,20,Fintricate maze reflecting his interest
OL,21,Fin geometric patterns.
OL,26,@sD@AOUsD@]O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
