CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1780275788
OL,3,CBalmoral 'a uniquely special place in
OL,4,Cthe hearts of the royal family', says
OL,5,CKing
OL,7,FWrought-iron gates in the Queen Mary's
OL,8,FGarden were remodelled in 2023 to
OL,9,Fcelebrate the centenary of their
OL,10,Fcreation and the coronation of Charles
OL,11,Fand Camilla with the inclusion of the
OL,12,Fcouple's cyphers.
OL,14,FInside the castle, the King has
OL,15,Fintroduced more furniture, paintings
OL,16,Fand objects, many drawn from the Royal
OL,17,FCollection, along with carpets.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1780275788
OL,3,CBalmoral 'a uniquely special place in
OL,4,Cthe hearts of the royal family', says
OL,5,CKing
OL,7,FMs Miers said: "Balmoral will forever
OL,8,Fbe associated with Victoria and
OL,9,FAlbert's love affair with the
OL,10,FHighlands, but there's so much more to
OL,11,Fthe story, which I hope this guidebook
OL,12,Freveals.
OL,26,@oD@POU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30310
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1780275788
OL,3,CBalmoral 'a uniquely special place in
OL,4,Cthe hearts of the royal family', says
OL,5,CKing
OL,7,F"Now that Balmoral is more publicly
OL,8,Faccessible, it's possible to
OL,9,Fappreciate how central the Prince
OL,10,FConsort's interests in architecture,
OL,11,Fdesign, landscaping and estate
OL,12,Fmanagement were to its creation, and
OL,13,Fhow effectively the King, who shares
OL,14,Fthese passions, has added a new layer
OL,15,Fof interest and style, while
OL,16,Fpreserving and enhancing the original."
OL,26,@oD@AOUxD@gO]
